<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Visitas - Pampa</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f4f8; min-height: 100vh; }

header {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a5c, #2d6a9f);
color: white; padding: 20px 24px; text-align: center;
box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}
header h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
header p { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.85; }
.badge { display:inline-block; background:#f0a500; color:white; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:bold; padding:2px 10px; border-radius:20px; margin-top:8px; }

.intro-box {
max-width:1100px; margin:20px auto 0; padding:0 20px;
}
.intro-inner {
background:white; border-radius:12px; padding:22px 24px;
box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-left:5px solid #2d6a9f;
}

.container { display:flex; gap:20px; padding:20px; max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; flex-wrap:wrap; }

.left-panel { flex:1 1 420px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px; }
.right-panel { flex:1 1 300px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px; }

.card { background:white; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
.card h2 { font-size:1rem; color:#1a3a5c; margin-bottom:14px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }

.form-row { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
label { font-size:0.85rem; color:#555; font-weight:600; }
input, select { width:100%; padding:9px 12px; border:1.5px solid #d0d9e4; border-radius:8px; font-size:0.9rem; background:#fafcff; transition:border 0.2s; }
input:focus { border-color:#2d6a9f; outline:none; }

.date-nav { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
.date-nav button { background:#e8f0f8; border:none; border-radius:8px; padding:8px 14px; cursor:pointer; font-size:1rem; color:#1a3a5c; transition:background 0.2s; }
.date-nav button:hover { background:#2d6a9f; color:white; }
.date-nav span { flex:1; text-align:center; font-weight:700; font-size:0.9rem; color:#1a3a5c; }

.slots-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:8px; margin-top:4px; }
.slot-btn { padding:8px 4px; border-radius:8px; border:2px solid #d0d9e4; background:white; cursor:pointer; font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:600; color:#333; transition:all 0.15s; text-align:center; }
.slot-btn:hover:not(.full):not(.past) { border-color:#2d6a9f; background:#e8f0f8; }
.slot-btn.selected { border-color:#2d6a9f; background:#2d6a9f; color:white; }
.slot-btn.full { background:#fce8e8; border-color:#e57373; color:#c0392b; cursor:not-allowed; }
.slot-btn.partial { border-color:#f0a500; background:#fff8e6; }
.slot-btn.past { opacity:0.4; cursor:not-allowed; }
.slot-count { display:block; font-weight:400; font-size:0.7rem; opacity:0.8; margin-top:2px; }

.legend { display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; font-size:0.75rem; color:#666; margin-top:8px; }
.legend-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; }
.legend-dot { width:12px; height:12px; border-radius:3px; border:2px solid transparent; }

.btn-register { width:100%; padding:12px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a3a5c,#2d6a9f); color:white; border:none; border-radius:10px; font-size:1rem; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; transition:opacity 0.2s; margin-top:4px; }
.btn-register:hover { opacity:0.9; }
.btn-register:disabled { opacity:0.5; cursor:not-allowed; }

.msg { padding:10px 14px; border-radius:8px; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; text-align:center; }
.msg.success { background:#e6f9ee; color:#2d7a4f; }
.msg.error { background:#fce8e8; color:#c0392b; }

.next-card { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a3a5c,#2d6a9f); color:white; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
.next-card h2 { font-size:0.9rem; opacity:0.85; margin-bottom:8px; }
.next-visit { font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:4px; }
.next-none { font-size:0.9rem; opacity:0.7; font-style:italic; }

.list-card { max-height:520px; overflow-y:auto; }
.list-card h2 { position:sticky; top:0; background:white; padding-bottom:10px; z-index:1; }

.visit-item { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #f0f4f8; gap:8px; }
.visit-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.visit-time { font-weight:800; font-size:0.85rem; color:#1a3a5c; min-width:90px; }
.visit-date-tag { font-size:0.7rem; color:#888; font-weight:400; display:block; }
.visit-names { font-size:0.82rem; color:#444; flex:1; }
.visit-badge { font-size:0.65rem; padding:2px 7px; border-radius:10px; font-weight:700; white-space:nowrap; }
.visit-badge.full { background:#fce8e8; color:#c0392b; }
.visit-badge.open { background:#e6f9ee; color:#2d7a4f; }
.delete-btn { background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; color:#ccc; font-size:1rem; padding:0 2px; transition:color 0.2s; }
.delete-btn:hover { color:#e57373; }
.empty-state { text-align:center; color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem; padding:20px 0; }

.tab-bar { display:flex; gap:0; margin-bottom:14px; border-bottom:2px solid #e8f0f8; }
.tab { flex:1; padding:8px; text-align:center; font-size:0.82rem; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; color:#888; border-bottom:3px solid transparent; margin-bottom:-2px; transition:all 0.15s; }
.tab.active { color:#1a3a5c; border-bottom-color:#2d6a9f; }

.spinner { text-align:center; color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem; padding:16px 0; }

@media (max-width:600px) { .slots-grid { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); } header h1 { font-size:1.3rem; } }
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>🏥 Visitas a Pampa</h1>
  <p>Coordiná tu visita — máximo 2 personas por turno</p>
  <span class="badge">Turnos de 30 minutos</span>
</header>

<div class="intro-box">
  <div class="intro-inner">
    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:#1a3a5c;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">💛 Hola a todos</p>
    <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#444;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:12px;">
      Pampa tiene muchas visitas y eso es hermoso — significa que es muy querido 🥹.<br>
      Para que no se junten todos a la vez y él pueda descansar entre visita y visita, armamos este pequeño organizador.<br>
      <strong>No es nada rígido ni obligatorio</strong>, solo una forma de coordinarnos un poco entre todos.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#555;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;">
      Elegís un horario que te quede cómodo, te anotás, y listo. Si después no podés ir, cancelás sin drama. Hasta 2 personas por turno.
    </p>
    <label style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.88rem;color:#333;">
      <input type="checkbox" id="agreeCheck" onchange="toggleForm()" style="width:18px;height:18px;margin-top:2px;accent-color:#2d6a9f;flex-shrink:0;">
      <span>Entiendo que esto es flexible y me comprometo a <strong>no hacer caprichito</strong> 😄 — si no puedo ir, cancelo mi turno para que otro pueda pasar.</span>
